  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial seeks to compare the effects of melatonin supplementation versus placebo in
      subjects with the metabolic syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of this Phase II crossover design trial is to examine the safety and
      efficacy of 8mg of melatonin taken one hour before bedtime compared to a placebo treatment to
      improve at least one of the five components associated with the metabolic syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
